      <doc xml:space="preserve"
           filename="libxfce4ui/xfce-icon-view.h"
           line="54">A function used for checking whether a row in @model matches a search key string
entered by the user. Note the return value is reversed from what you would normally
expect, though it has some similarity to strcmp() returning 0 for equal strings.</doc>
